    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      72.48,
      543.2,
      87.52
    ],
    "text": "In terms of Section 28(4A) of the Local Authorities Elections Ordinance it is",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0,
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      95.78,
      542.87,
      110.82
    ],
    "text": "abundantly clear that a certified copy of the birth certificate of every youth candidate",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      119.18,
      314.33,
      134.22
    ],
    "text": "should be tendered which reads as follows;",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      150.02,
      542.95,
      199.83
    ],
    "text": "(4A) A certified copy of the birth Certificate of every youth whose name appears in the nomination paper or an affidavit signed by such youth, certifying his date of birth shall be attached to such nomination paper.",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua-BoldItalic",
      "BookAntiqua-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      210.74,
      542.99,
      225.78
    ],
    "text": "Given that the statutory provision is clear and unambiguous, all parties and",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      234.14,
      543.07,
      249.18
    ],
    "text": "candidates must adhere to it strictly. The legislative intent is explicit, the copy of the",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      257.45,
      543.22,
      272.49
    ],
    "text": "birth certificate must be certified by a legally authorized person. In the present case,",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      280.73,
      543.01,
      295.77
    ],
    "text": "the Petitioner admittedly submitted uncertified photocopies, which contravene the",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      304.13,
      249.29,
      319.17
    ],
    "text": "express requirement of the law.",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      335.33,
      543.0,
      350.37
    ],
    "text": "It is pertinent to note that permitting mere photocopies of birth certificates, without",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      358.61,
      543.11,
      373.65
    ],
    "text": "certification by a legally authorized person, opens the door to potential fraud, forgery,",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      381.89,
      542.99,
      396.93
    ],
    "text": "and manipulation. Unlike certified copies, which bear an official seal or attestation",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      405.17,
      543.13,
      420.21
    ],
    "text": "confirming their authenticity, ordinary photocopies can be altered, tampered with, or",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      428.59,
      542.92,
      443.63
    ],
    "text": "falsified without detection. The very purpose of certification is to safeguard against",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      451.87,
      542.98,
      466.91
    ],
    "text": "such risks, when a certifying officer examines the original document and endorses the",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      475.15,
      542.95,
      490.19
    ],
    "text": "copy, they verify its accuracy and create a legally enforceable record of its",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      498.43,
      542.74,
      513.47
    ],
    "text": "authenticity. Without this step, there is no assurance that the submitted documents",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      521.83,
      423.07,
      536.87
    ],
    "text": "are genuine, undermining the integrity of the electoral process.",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      553.03,
      542.87,
      568.07
    ],
    "text": "I am unable to agree with the observation of Tilakawardane, J. in the aforementioned",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      576.31,
      542.76,
      591.35
    ],
    "text": "case that a mere photocopy of a birth certificate suffices for compliance with",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      599.62,
      542.87,
      614.66
    ],
    "text": "nomination requirements. With respect, this interpretation runs contrary to the",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      623.02,
      542.79,
      638.06
    ],
    "text": "express language of Section 28(4A) of the Local Authorities Elections Ordinance,",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      646.3,
      543.22,
      661.34
    ],
    "text": "which explicitly mandates the submission of a certified copy of the birth certificate.",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      669.58,
      542.83,
      684.62
    ],
    "text": "The statutory provision leaves no room for ambiguity, the legislature in its wisdom",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      729.22,
      311.76,
      755.86
    ],
    "text": "4",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      72.48,
      542.77,
      87.52
    ],
    "text": "has imposed this requirement precisely to ensure the authenticity of documentation",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      95.9,
      204.17,
      110.94
    ],
    "text": "in the electoral process.",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      127.1,
      542.76,
      142.14
    ],
    "text": "Similarly, to the extent that the guideline issued by the Election Commissioner",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      150.38,
      542.89,
      165.42
    ],
    "text": "purports to permit the submission of uncertified copies of birth certificates, such",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      173.66,
      542.81,
      188.7
    ],
    "text": "direction is fundamentally inconsistent with the clear provisions of Section 28(4A).",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      197.06,
      542.9,
      212.1
    ],
    "text": "Administrative guidelines cannot override or dilute substantive statutory",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      220.34,
      542.86,
      235.38
    ],
    "text": "requirements. Consequently, that portion of the guideline which suggests that",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      243.62,
      543.18,
      258.66
    ],
    "text": "uncertified copies are acceptable has no legal force or validity, being ultra vires the",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua",
      "BookAntiqua-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      267.05,
      174.62,
      282.09
    ],
    "text": "parent legislation.",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.479999542236328
    ]
